---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Three-Letter Words — Scrabble Blog"
  description="Complete guide to three-letter words in Scrabble. High-scoring plays, strategy tips, printable lists, and words with Q and Z. Free, no signup required."
  keywords="three letter scrabble words, 3 letter words scrabble, best three letter words, three letter words with q, three letter words with z, scrabble short words, high scoring three letter words"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why are three-letter words important in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Three-letter words let you play parallel to existing words, creating multiple scoring opportunities in a single turn. They also help you manage your rack by using awkward letter combinations without wasting a full turn." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How many valid three-letter words are there in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "There are over 1,000 valid three-letter words in the Official Scrabble Players Dictionary (OSPD) and the Tournament Word List (TWL). Learning even 100-200 of the most useful ones gives you a significant edge." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are the highest-scoring three-letter words?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Words like ZAX (19 points), ZEK (16 points), QAT (12 points), and ZAP (14 points) score highly because they use premium tiles. Placing them on double or triple letter squares multiplies their value even further." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
      <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
      <span class="mx-1">›</span>
      <span class="text-gray-300">Three-Letter Words</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Three-Letter Words</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
      Three-letter words are the backbone of smart Scrabble play. They let you hook onto existing words,
      clear difficult tiles, and score in tight spaces. These 10 guides cover everything from high-scoring
      picks to printable lists and strategy — all designed to sharpen your short-word game.
    </p>

    <!-- Post grid -->
    <div class="grid gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/best-three-letter-scrabble-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best Three-Letter Scrabble Words for High Scores</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The top three-letter words ranked by point value — maximise your score with short, powerful plays.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/common-three-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Common Three-Letter Words Every Player Needs</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The most frequently played three-letter words in competitive Scrabble — essential vocabulary for any level.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/highest-scoring-three-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Highest Scoring Three-Letter Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">A ranked list of the most valuable three-letter plays, including premium square strategies.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/three-letter-words-with-q" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Three-Letter Words With Q</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Every valid three-letter Q word — including those that don't need a U. Essential for clearing the Q tile.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/three-letter-words-with-z" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Three-Letter Words With Z</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">All valid three-letter Z words to help you use the 10-point Z tile effectively in tight board positions.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/easy-three-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Easy Three-Letter Words to Learn First</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Start with the simplest, most intuitive three-letter words — build your vocabulary without overwhelm.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/three-letter-word-strategy" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Three-Letter Word Strategy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">How to use three-letter words tactically — parallel plays, hooks, rack management, and board control.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/printable-three-letter-list" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Printable Three-Letter Word List</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">A clean, printable reference of all valid three-letter Scrabble words — perfect for study sessions.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/overlooked-three-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Most Overlooked Three-Letter Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Hidden gems that most players miss — unusual but valid words that can turn a losing rack into a winning play.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/three-letter-words-for-beginners" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Three-Letter Words for Beginners</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">A gentle introduction to three-letter words for new players — what to learn first and how to practise.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Links to other category pages -->
    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">More Categories</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/two-letter-words" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Two-Letter Words — Master the 127 essential short words</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/beginner-guides" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Beginner Guides — Learn Scrabble from scratch</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/strategy" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Strategy — Advanced tactics and rack management</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/high-scoring" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">High-Scoring Words — The most valuable plays in Scrabble</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA box -->
    <div class="mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-indigo-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">
          🔍 Find three-letter words instantly with our free word finder
        </p>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm"
        >
          Open Word Finder →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
